If you will con\nsider the experience of others under\nsimilar circumstances, who have been\nmost successful in checking their\ncolds, in their beginning, you will\nsecure a bottle of Chamberlain's\nCough Remedy without lelay, and\nuse it faithfully. There are many\nfamilies who have used this prepara\ntion successful I v for years and hold\nit in high esteem. It is excellent.\nDu You\nKnow that Medical\nAuthorities tell us that\none person out cf every\nfour is suffering from\nsome form of heart dis\norder?\nPossibly you Tray he troubled\nwith some ailment of the heart\nand not know it.\u2014Smothering,\nShortness of breath. Fainting\nSpells, Irregular Pulse, Chok\ning Sensr.tion, Nightmare\nThese are a few of the dange\nsignals of Heart Trouble. For\nmany years\nDR. MILES\u2019\nHeart Treatment\nHas been used with great sue\ncess and has reliev'd a..d\nbenefited thousands of people.\nIf you have any wet I ues\u00bb,\nirregularity or distress cf the\nheart dorct wait until its too\nlate\u2014ACT NOW.\nBuy a bottle of tnit tins.\ntested medicine todxy. Mon y\nback if first bottle fails to re\nlieve.\nSOLD BY ALL DRUGGETS\n1 nfESSIM oil\nrURION F. RhID\nATTORNEY-AT-LAW I\nHurley,\nGeo. C. Foster VV. B. Fowl\nFOSTER FOSTER j\nAttorneys at Law K\nOffice over Paul's Store Phone 843-11\nC. C. URQUHART, M. 1)1\nPHYSICIAN AND SURGEON I\nOffice over Paul's store. I\n10 to 11 a. m., 2 to 3 and 7 to 8 p. m\nPhone No. 610-2\nHurley, Wstl\nF. G. VAN STRATUM\nand SON\nSURGEON DENTISTS\nHurley, V:i|\nW.C TREZONA\nSURGEON DENTIST\nHurley, 'Vie\nflL If you need\nw some coue\n\"Bills \"J:\nREID\u2019S\nREAL ESTATE AND\nINSURANCE OFFICE\nEstablished 1886\nBONDS LOANS\nFIRE\nBURGLARY\nACCIDENT\nand EMPLOYER\u2019S\nLIABILITY\nINSURANCE\nNone but the Strongest Insurance\nCompanies in this Agency.\nJOE. POLLOCK\nPluinblng, Meat log\nand\nRepairing\nEstimates furnished\n-All Work Guaranteed.\nShop at\nHammond hotel Bids:.","height":"28378","width":"18542"}}
